DA SCHLOP

Each item costs 1 ZORK, except a SchynKLE which costs 3 ZORKs. Items may only be bought once!

    Sclankle: With this you can deny 1 drink per phase (Except a JORKLE of course)

    Sclenke: Using this activates Mr.Spillalge, Mr.Spillage must take x2 the drinks given to them. If a player makes a party foul, they become Mr.Spillage. The player chooses who becomes Mr.Spillage first.

    Sclinkle: Ban one noun from being used for the rest of the game. If a player says the given noun they take a drink. Sclinkle holder is exempt from this rule.

    Schlonkle: Play a Beer of Rights Game of your choosing. Winner gets 4 points, loser takes a shot.

    Schlunkle: Get 1 JORKLE.

    SchynKLE: Add one rule to JORKLE SPUNK (must not break the game).

DA SCHLOP 2: Double The Slopage

Players can convert their ZORKS into SLOP! The conversion rate is 4 ZORKS = 1 SLOP! Each item may only be bought once, and players cannot convert their SLOPs back into ZORKs.

    Baby JORKLE : 1 SLOP : Using this you can give a player of your choosing a cup with 2 shots in it. The player reciving this cup looses 4 points.

    DOUBLE SchynKLE : 1 SLOP + 1 ZORK : Player recives 2 SchynKLEs.

    10 Points : 2 SLOP : Self Explanatory

    EDBCC JORKLE : 2 SLOP : Allows a you to JORKLE an opposing player, but you are allowed to add 1 shot of liquor and 1 shot of any mixer to the cup.

    ONE WISH : 3 SLOP : Allows a player to choose any one reward from the JORKLE SPUNK SCRIPTURE. Rewards are given as if the player had one first place(where applicable). Does not work on rewards more expensive than it.

    STICKY POCKET : 4 SLOP : You can steal 5 points from all the remaining players.

    DEATH JORKLE : 6 SLOP : Allows a player to remove all of an opposing players points, and JORKLE them.

